text: Geronimo "Ronnie" Dyogi was a judoka from Philippines. Geronimo competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics. He was born on 20 July 1949 and died on 23 July 2016.Geronimo Dyogi == References == Category:1949 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Olympians for the Philippines Category:Judoka Category:Sportspeople from Manila
